				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7707753#post-4526004</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7707753/scp-4626#post-4526004</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 01 Mar 2020 21:13:07 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Squamous</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3484071</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I could leave the stuff about the GoI religious groups, and think I'd rather they were people previously affected by 4626 going to ridiculous lengths to try and contain it: I feel like the stone <em>actually</em> being really important and dangerous undermines the beauty of what otherwise feels like fairly meta commentary about some of the 'big, unique, special and dangerous' SCPs on the site, what with the mass panic it generates, the non-standard containment class and the masses of overblown containment procedures.<br /> Definitely still a +1 though!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
